Summary: saw very faint light objects in sky very dim and small moving slowly across sky
divs: Sighting Detailswas driving home from work pulled over to look at skies on bypass..saw very faint dimly light lights in north west skies..they were slowly moving further north west ..they covered a large portion of the sky..but could not see anything else it was very dark and black skies that night..so i took pictures and blew them up and it looks like an oil rig in the sky..maybe military im not sure
